                                               ASSIGNMENT-1

Q.1 Write a simple program in HTML that displays the heading "HTML defines the content 
    and structure of your website" on the web browser?

Ans-Program-
     <!DOCTYPE html>
     <html>
       <head>
       <meta charset="UTF-8">
       <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
       <title>HTML Heading</title>
       </head>
     <body>
      <h1>HTML defines the content and structure of your website</h1>
     </body>
    </html>

Q.2 Explain the purpose of comments in HTML and provide an expamle of how to use comments in an HTML document?
Ans-We use comments in html for documentation or for expalination.
   Example- <body>
                 <!--This is a heading for my web page. The comment is not visible on page. -->
                  <h1>Hello, Guys I am Aashish></h1>
                </body>

Q.3 Write an Html program that includes a heading,a paragraph of a text, a horizontal line, and a line break.
    Arrange these elements to create a simple web page layout?

Ans- Example-Program
        <html>
        <head>
          <meta charset="UTF-8">
          <title>My page</title>
          </head>
         <body>
             <h1>Assignment Heading</h1>
             <p>I am Aashish Srivastava.I am a coder and a student of pw skills.</p><br>
                <hr>
              <p>Currently I am persuing B.tech Computer science From punjab technical university.</p>
               </body>           

Q.4 Write a short note on Tag and element with an example?

Ans->Tag- It defines the structure and content of web page.It consists of angled brackets '<' and '>'.
    Example-Heading tag- <h1> , Paragraph tag - <p> etc.

    Element- It is the combination of all Opening,closing tag and content also.
     Example- <h1> Hello World<h1> , <p> This is a beautiful building</p> etc.

Q.5 What is the DOCTYPE Declaration in  HTML?

Ans- The DOCTYPE declaration in HTML , typically written as <! DOCTYPE html>. 
     It specifies the version of Html used in web document. It ensure the compatibility with the web browser.
